        <argsstring>()</argsstring>
        <name>~wxThreadHelper</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>The destructor frees the resources associated with the thread, forcing it to terminate (it uses <ref refid="classwx_thread_1a2cbff8b3b0a93ab82f212c02f38a1ef4" kindref="member">wxThread::Kill</ref> function). </para>
